<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.10">
<l>vañcaṉaiyāl vanta pēycci mulaiyuṇṭa</l>
<l>vañcaṉa vaṇṇaṉai yāyccitā lāṭṭiya</l>
<l>ceñcol maṟaiyavar cērputuvaip paṭṭaṉco</l>
<l>leñcāmai vallavark killai yiṭartāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no affliction for those who master without deficiency</l>
<l>the words of the scholar of Putuvai who lives among brahmins of correct language</l>
<l>that the Cowherdess sang while rocking [to sleep] the kohl coloured</l>
<l>one who drank [from] the breast of the demoness who had come with lies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
